ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2261450763","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2261450763","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjI2MTQ1MDc2Mw==","status":"current","title":"Infrastructure","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":274390946},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2261450763/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2261450763/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2261450763/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2261450763/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2261450763","tinyui":"/x/CwDLhg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2261450763","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2261450763/Infrastructure","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2261450763"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Este documento proporciona los pasos detallados para facilitar el proceso de solicitud de un usuario SSH, permiti&eacute;ndote acceder de manera segura a nuestros servidores de producci&oacute;n.</p><p>Recordar que estos usuarios solo ser&aacute;n necesarios para acceder a los servidores de <strong>producci&oacute;n</strong>. Para acceder a los servidores de staging podremos utilizar los usuarios IPA personales.</p><h2>Pasos para la Solicitud</h2><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Ingresar al siguiente link: <a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/16/group/29/create/99\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://bancard.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/16/group/29/create/99</a> <br /></p></li><li><p>Al ingresar al link, ver&aacute; el siguiente formulario de solicitud.</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"895\" ac:original-width=\"733\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"733\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20231128-154005.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /><ac:adf-mark key=\"border\" size=\"1\" color=\"#091e4224\" /></ac:image><p>Debe completar el formulario con los siguientes datos (algunos ya se encontrar&aacute;n seleccionados):<br /><br /><strong>Contact us about:</strong> Monitoreo - Solicitudes<br /><strong>What can we help you with?:</strong> Gesti&oacute;n de usuarios para PRD<br /><strong>Resumen:</strong> Solicitud de usuario SSH para producci&oacute;n<br /><strong>Seleccione el sistema al que acceder&aacute;:</strong> Servidores Linux<br /><strong>Descripci&oacute;n:</strong> Usuario para acceder a ambiente de producci&oacute;n para el equipo desarrollo de Qubika, utilizado para configuraci&oacute;n, an&aacute;lisis de inconvenientes en producci&oacute;n y revisiones peri&oacute;dicas.<br /></p></li><li><p>Luego de enviar el formulario y de que alguien del equipo de Bancard pueda completar la solicitud, recibir&aacute; en su correo un usuario v&aacute;lido por 3 d&iacute;as para acceder a los servidores de producci&oacute;n:</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"258\" ac:original-width=\"747\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"736\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Screenshot 2023-11-28 at 12.54.00-20231128-155627.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image></li></ol><p /><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>MISSION ACCOMPLISHED! </strong><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":white_check_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"2705\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"✅\" /></p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2791309687"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":1481},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2791309687/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2791309687/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2791309687/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2791309687/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2791309687","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2791309687/Solicitud+de+Usuario+SSH+Producci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2791309687","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2791309687","tinyui":"/x/dwFgpg","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}